window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Ron was just a trucker with a long haul ahead until he wakes up in a strange fantasy realm.</b></p> <p>He's relocated to Kario, a place where magic levels up one mana point at a time and dangerous fiends prowl the roads at night. Ron's sent to help improve the odds for the human kingdoms as a trading magus, a caravan master who's able to bend magic to his will.</p> <p>Mythical forces are on the march as they raid, pillage, and siege cities across the land. A horde of enemy heroes, and too few trying to keep them at bay. To fulfill his quest he'll form a merchant caravan to aid those in need, turn danger into profit, and forge a life as the Wandering Magus King.</p>"; 
